Q8u8UBcrdluPwVyyiZBMsCffWZXRq1fmHnUCpw&oe=671E277F"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "Cover Art.png", "id": "1879180449246011", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031622_1879180452579344_2466503368485128699_n.png?_nc_cat=110&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=oayF7xZKh6sQ7kNvgEzuwaN&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYC6IUI8ygHvnwNLv3Smg01_kSfUAWgElSF-jY3EvYS3hw&oe=671E1E7C"}, "display_name": "Memory Palace", "keywords": [], "long_description": "# Your Living Room: The Second Brain\n\n\n\nImagine turning your living room into a powerful tool for your memory. With **Your Living Room: The Second Brain**, you can do just that. This game uses the ancient Memory Palace technique, a method that dates back to the Roman Empire. By linking information to specific spots in your living room, you can remember things more easily and have fun while doing it.\n\n\n### Why It Helps\n\n1. **Scientifically Proven**: The Memory Palace technique is backed by science. It helps you make strong mental connections, making it easier to remember stuff.\n2. **Ancient Wisdom**: Romans used this method to remember long speeches and complex information. If it worked for them, it can work for you too.\n3. **Competitive and training mode**: This game turns your living room into a mental playground. By using 3D objects and voice memos, you make memorization more engaging and enjoyable.\n\n\n### Examples of Data You Can Save\n\n- To-Do Lists\n- Study Notes\n- Important Dates\n- Language Vocabulary\n- Meeting Agendas\n- Personal Goals\n- Shopping Lists\n- Product Pitches\n- Presentations\n- Keynote Text\n- Important Conversations\n\n## Why You Should Try It\n\nMake your memory work for you with **Your Living Room: The Second Brain**. Turn your everyday space into a dynamic tool for learning and personal growth. Start using it today and see how much more you can remember!\n\n{361819590133965}", "short_description": "Can you walk through your living room in your head, even when you are at school? \n\nWelcome to your second brain, your living room! Use your furniture to save voice memos and memorize anything you want. You can save and train, and use 3d objects for guidance."}]}, "developer_name": "augmented camel", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://augmentedcamel.notion.site/MEMORY-PALACE-5115fed423dc49ae852ca87491c8298c?pvs=4", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Digital Dromedaries", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://mmm.page/camels/memorypalace", "category": null, "comfort_rating": null, "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "362692211442873", "context_category": "APPS"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "1063584910766706"}, {"id": "879473995923081"}, {"id": "421923165850360"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["HAND_TRACKING"], "supported_player_modes": ["ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "7978793018871680"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 1, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1192758131828553"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "1192758131828553"}, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": [{"start_time": 1723665032, "status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1192758131828553"}]}, "liveChannel": {"nodes": [{"latest_supported_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "id": "7895969577154025", "version": "1.0.0"}, "id": "1969953126784709", "channel_name": "LIVE"}]}, "is_for_oculus_keys_only": false, "primary_binaries": {"nodes": [{"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "7819646968119620", "is_concept": fals